	(12,127,'prof-anthony','Senior QA','<p>Test 123</p>','<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Anthony Oluwafemi Olaseni Joshua</strong>,&nbsp;<span class=\"noexcerpt\" style=\"font-size: 11.9px;\"><a class=\"mw-redirect\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"Member of the Order of the British Empire\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Member_of_the_Order_of_the_British_Empire\">MBE</a></span>&nbsp;(born 15 October 1989) is a British&nbsp;<a class=\"mw-redirect\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"Professional boxer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Professional_boxer\">professional boxer</a>. He is currently a unified world&nbsp;<a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"Heavyweight\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heavyweight\">heavyweight</a>&nbsp;champion, having held the&nbsp;<a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"International Boxing Federation\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Boxing_Federation\">IBF</a>&nbsp;title since 2016, and the&nbsp;<a class=\"mw-redirect\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"WBA (Super)\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WBA_(Super)\">WBA (Super)</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"International Boxing Organization\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Boxing_Organization\">IBO</a>&nbsp;titles since April 2017. At regional level he held the&nbsp;<a style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\" title=\"British Boxing Board of Control\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\">British</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class=\"mw-redirect\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: non