al level he held the&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"British Boxing Board of Control\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\\\">British<\\/a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Commonwealth Boxing Council\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\\\">Commonwealth<\\/a>&nbsp;heavyweight titles from 2015 to 2016. As an&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Amateur boxing\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Amateur_boxing\\\">amateur<\\/a>, Joshua represented Britain at the&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"2012 Olympics\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/2012_Olympics\\\">2012 Olympics<\\/a>, winning a gold medal in the&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Super-heavyweight\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Super-heavyweight\\\">super-heavyweight<\\/a>&nbsp;division; he also represented England at the&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"2011 AIBA World Boxing Championships\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/2011_AIBA_World_Boxing_Championships\\\">2011 World Championships<\\/a>, winning silver. In 2014,&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"The Ring magazine\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/The_Ring_magazine\\\"><em>The Ring<\\/em>&nbsp;magazine<\\/a>&nbsp;named him their&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"The Ring magazine Prospect of the Year\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/The_Ring_magazine_Prospect_of_the_Year\\\">Prospect of the Year<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0.5em 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #222222; font-family: sans-serif;\\\">As of May 2017, Joshua is ranked as the world\'s best heavyweight by the&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Transnational Boxing Rankings Board\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Transnational_Boxing_Rankings_Board\\\">Transnational Boxing Rankings Board<\\/a><sup id=\\\"cite_ref-TNRBratings0010a_1-0\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\\\"><a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Anthony_Joshua#cite_note-TNRBratings0010a-1\\\">[1]<\\/a><\\/sup>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"BoxRec\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/BoxRec\\\">BoxRec<\\/a>,<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-ReferenceA_2-0\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\\\"><a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Anthony_Joshua#cite_note-ReferenceA-2\\\">[2]<\\/a><\\/sup>&nbsp;and second best by&nbsp;<em>The Ring<\\/em>.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-3\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\\\"><a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Anthony_Joshua#cite_note-3\\\">[3]<\\/a><\\/sup>&nbsp;His&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Knockout\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Knockout\\\">