.org\\/wiki\\/International_Boxing_Organization\\\">IBO<\\/a>&nbsp;titles since April 2017. At regional level he held the&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"British Boxing Board of Control\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\\\">British<\\/a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Commonwealth Boxing Council\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\\\">Commonwealth<\\/a>&nbsp;heavyweight titles from 2015 to 2016. As an&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Amateur boxing\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Amateur_boxing\\\">amateur<\\/a>, Joshua represented Britain at the&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"2012 Olympics\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/2012_Olympics\\\">2012 Olympics<\\/a>, winning a gold medal in the&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"Super-heavyweight\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Super-heavyweight\\\">super-heavyweight<\\/a>&nbsp;division; he also represented England at the&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"2011 AIBA World Boxing Championships\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/2011_AIBA_World_Boxing_Championships\\\">2011 World Championships<\\/a>, winning silver. In 2014,&nbsp;<a class=\\\"mw-redirect\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration-line: none; color: #0b0080; background: none;\\\" title=\\\"The Ring magazine\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/The_Ring_magazine\\\"><em>The Ring<\\/em>&nbsp;magazine<\\/a>&nbsp;named him their&nbsp;<a style=\\\"text-dec